Usage: deleteMimCap [-help] [{[-cell <string>] [-prefix <string>]} [-area {x1 y1 x2 y2}]]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-area {x1 y1 x2 y2}     # area (box, optional)
-cell <string>          # cell name (string, optional)
-prefix <string>        # prefix name (string, optional)